<img src="//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/3/e/8/3e84ae4877306fe31c437c72a984f957272014f1.png" class="latexcenter" alt="\[ \frac {1}{\sqrt {h}} \geq \frac {1}{\sqrt {AD}} + \frac {1}{\sqrt {BC}}
